data.description: 2 story 4 BR 3 Bath contemporary Fischer home with open floor design, 2 wood decks, walk-out unfinished basement, tinted stamped concrete patio and attached 2 car garage located on a semi-private densely wooded lot leading down to a creek with no development on the other side. No HOA fees. Family room and entryway are open to the second floor ceiling.  One bedroom is downstairs with full bathroom.
data.whatILove: I love the privacy, location and view of nature via the wall of windows. Family-friendly neighborhood with lots of sidewalks and shade trees.
